General.Name: Critical Resources Ltd
General.Description: Critical Resources Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral projects. The company explores for lithium, zinc, lead, copper, silver, and gold deposits. Critical Resources Limited was formerly known as Force Commodities Limited and changed its name to Critical Resources Limited in May 2021. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Perth, Australia.
